content:
Use the Additional AWS Services Add-on License to include additional AWS services in Service Cloud Voice with Amazon Connect.

This feature is available with these telephony models:

SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH AMAZON CONNECT	SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY FROM AMAZON CONNECT	SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY

With the Additional AWS Services Add-on License, you have the option to access these AWS services for your contact center.

SERVICE	WHAT YOU CAN DO
Amazon API Gateway	Create, maintain, and secure APIs at any scale.
Amazon CloudWatch (included with purchase)	Observe and monitor resources and applications on AWS.
Amazon Connect Voice ID	Real-time caller authentication and fraud risk detection using ML-powered voice analysis.
Amazon Dynamo DB (included with purchase)	Fast, flexible NoSQL database service for single-digit millisecond performance at any scale.
Amazon EventBridge (included with purchase)	Build event-driven applications at scale across AWS.
Amazon GuardDuty	Protect your AWS accounts with intelligent threat detection.
Amazon Kinesis Data Firehose	Reliably load real-time streams into data lakes, warehouses, and analytics services.
Amazon Pinpoint	Connect with customers through scalable, targeted multichannel communications.
Amazon SES	Get reliable, scalable email to communicate with customers at the lowest industry prices.
Amazon Simple Notification Service (SNS) (included with purchase)	Fully managed Pub/Sub service for A2A and A2P messaging.
AWS Direct Connect	Create a dedicated network connection to AWS.
AWS PrivateLink	Establish connectivity between VPCs and AWS services without exposing data to the internet.
title: Maximizing Service Cloud Voice with Additional AWS Services
